Birmingham Road,<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>Sutton Coldfield,
West Midlands, B72 1YL</p>
<p class="MsoFooter" style="margin-bottom:12.0pt;tab-stops:36.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">A4
with horrible side-staples, 20 pages, 7/8 weekly, 60p including postage<o:p>
</o:p>
