<p class="MsoNormal"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-ansi-language:EN-US">Mango</span></b><span lang="EN-US" style="mso-ansi-language:EN-US">
comes in an unusual format - A4 folded in three to give the DL size and even
